title: Best Of The Dan Patrick Show: 12/17/202023
itunes:title: Best Of The Dan Patrick Show: 12/17/202023
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP continues to try to make sense of the College Playoffs Rankings. Is this season an indication that we'll never see a non Power 5 school in the playoffs, in this current format? We're joined by ESPN NBA reporter Tim MacMahon, Raven's Kicker Justin Tucker and Alabama Head Football Coach Nick Saban.
